English: The first wave of the war was the sea, but as radar technology developed and became more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen.

Central Kurdish: لە سەرەتای جەنگەکەدا بە گشتی دەچونە سەر ئاوەکە، بەڵام لەگەڵ پەرەدان بە ڕادار و باشترکارکردنی ب
clean_output: The first wave of the war was the sea, but as radar technology developed and became more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen.
